Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:03.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:05.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们在做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一眼就能明白吧  在做饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个  不觉得做的很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:13.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,皱褶很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:17.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我说  离截稿日期不是只剩六小时了么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:19.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:20.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好啦  你也来做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:28.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个是不是很完美？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:29.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有一手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:30.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不愧是师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:36.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这就是传说中的截稿期前的逃避现实么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:40.43,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)\bord3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H373745&\pos(742,794)}截稿期前的逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有时  被逼上绝路的漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会突然的开始改变房间的布局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:45.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,或者突然开始做起豪华大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以及开始打扫平时绝对不会管的换气扇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,此外  可能是因为罪恶感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:55.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比起像游戏以及娱乐用的活动  大多都是家务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好了  干活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:03.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不煎一下么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:04.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,煎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:07.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这种事在原稿完成后也能做吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:08.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,总算赶上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:16.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不如说  要是不做饺子会更从容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:19.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是因为做了饺子才赶上的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:21.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你这门外汉！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:25.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂啊
