Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在  我们来到了临海学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.99,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：临海学校是指学校组织的夏季海边合宿活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我说  帽子要好好戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.38,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz335.7\pos(1004,576)}沙滩凉鞋和B4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.63,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord4\c&H494956&\pos(932,680)}两天前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸做的咖喱甜甜的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:21.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸后天就休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以带姬去想去的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:30.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后天我要去临海学校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我怎么没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.90,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H51545F&\1a&H0D&\frz25.75\move(471.2,636.4,560,644)}临海学校的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:35.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一个月之前就发了通知单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,过  过去要多加小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们会去游泳  捉虫  还有办篝火哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:45.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:46.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,捉虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,办篝火？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好担心  好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以及  好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去海边职员旅行还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家都到极限了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,忘掉漫画的事情  好好地休整一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天会住在哪儿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,从熟人漫画家那儿借来的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还真肯借出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,多亏了镰仓病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:19.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然今天去的是千叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,镰仓病？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:22.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很早之前就得以广传
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫画家为了逃避现实所引发的现象之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:32.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,某个漫画家疲于每周的截稿日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:37.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,妄想着有一天能在海边悠闲地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:42.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后终于他在镰仓买了工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  从这之后才是恐怖的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为太远了助手不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,店铺关门太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为潮气导致笔尖生锈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:59.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最后他从梦中惊醒  逃回了东京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:00.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:04.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,从漫画家那儿借来多余的别墅才会如此简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来…如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:12.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,都说了别谈漫画的事情了会变阴暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这  这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,结果是被叫过来做清洁么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样的话就跟截稿日前的逃避现实没区别了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  老师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来这儿真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:33.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可疑人士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:42.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您在这儿做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,职员旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,碰巧合宿的地方就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,于是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就很在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为  实在太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可爱什么的  好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那当然可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.75,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(465,745.2)}在说姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.75,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1500.2,748.6)}在说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这件事请对姬保密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:13.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在这之后还得带孩子们去捉独角仙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,独角仙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.69,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz286.7\pos(1380.8,177.6)\c&H66656E&}起哄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.69,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz288.5\pos(969.6,243.2)\c&H66656E&}起哄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是只有姬没有捉到会不会被欺负？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:22.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个  我真的可爱么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,芥子君  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:27.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去买独角仙回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,买尽可能大只的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.74,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H486EC8&\3c&HE5E5E7&\pos(880,49.6)}宠物天国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.74,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H6D7788&\pos(742.4,601.6)}槌之子进货
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:37.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好  把这个放在姬捉得到的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:41.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有谁会买赫克力士大兜虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:41.21,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：赫克力斯大兜虫是世界上最长的甲虫，也是全世界最大的甲虫之一，分布于中南美洲的热带雨林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你不说过买尽可能大只的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:46.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小女孩在千叶捉到了这种虫会上新闻的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.05,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H454041&\frz13.64\pos(681.6,172.8)}在千叶县内发现了赫克力士大兜虫！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.05,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H444142&\pos(1504,403.2)\frz288.1}临海学校中的小学生发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.05,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H484547&\frz15.6\pos(558.4,920)}被发现的赫克力士大兜虫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:51.43,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)\fs60\c&HF7E1BB&\3c&H231818&\pos(137.6,56)}有赫克力士大兜虫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被发现作弊  然后被全国上下批判该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管虫子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其他的也很令人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可疑人士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  又下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没  还是很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个  因为很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请不要说两遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:09.19,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord5\c&H5CE8F1&\3c&H2127A3&\pos(257.6,110.4)}脸红
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,顺带一提这之后的安排是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:12.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我星期天会在家无所事事  空着的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我说孩子们的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他们在准备晚饭的咖喱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:21.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,顺带一提姬因为要负责调味而干劲十足哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,调味？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.83,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz268.9\pos(1795.2,281.6)\c&H90969F&}好难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.83,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270.7\pos(1297.6,204.8)\c&H90969F&}好难吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.83,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&HDFAACA&\3c&H9F8AA7&\pos(1009.6,670.4)}呜呜呜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,任性的请求不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:32.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事  我的儿子是「鸡鸡复鸡鸡」的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\i1\c&H474144&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1000,126.4)}现在话题中的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\bord3\frz7.293\3c&H775DBA&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1078.4,278.4)}咖喱店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 8 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\frz270\c&H494349&\pos(1139.2,440)}香料的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H51526F&\frz25.41\pos(1052.8,852.8)}那美味让人无法自拔！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad1\frz33.8\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H565775&\4c&H525572&\pos(232,401.6)}这个咖喱好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs45\c&H6E94C2&\frz258.3\pos(1624,518.4)}超越了咖喱的常识
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H6D92C9&\frz348.3\pos(1523.2,798.4)}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交给您一定没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬  来帮忙淘米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:44.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那摩斯戴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.11,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：梵语里的问候语，意为「向你鞠躬致敬」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.77,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H2114EC&\3c&H6DC6EC&\frz11.84\pos(377.6,313.6)}完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:45.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,两次说我可爱什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:54.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道说后藤老师对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是不行哦  一子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那可是学生的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是那样的哦  后藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:03.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要搅起来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,妈妈没教过你么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗  我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可疑人士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  有在好好干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她一直都是那副像是什么都没在思考的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,见笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉不是什么都没思考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是有意装作什么都没思考的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对不起  说了多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:46.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是您看  世上不是也有许多思考后也无法改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,无可奈何的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:52.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,思考后也无法改变的  无可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:57.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像是母亲的事情  以及我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有意装作没在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:06.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说不定孩子也在用孩子的方式去逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  您去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,别说玩了  连食欲都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,筋疲力尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:20.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明是来休息的这也太惨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这  这儿又有海又有山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明天连同今天的份一起玩个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大海  难得买好了泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在山上烧烤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.22,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs80\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HDEA568&\pos(379.2,316.8)}台风消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.22,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\shad3\c&HB1654F&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\pos(939.2,785.6)}「绝型」{\b0}蹂躏关东地区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:44.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太惨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那你们多加小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬她们中止了临海学校的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,似乎明早就会回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:56.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是因为台风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:59.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以不要在室内穿泳装么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行么  难得买都买了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这天气什么都干不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,别说大海了  一步都出不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:10.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,停电？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,手机电池用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:24.56,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}懒懒散散
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,电视和游戏都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:18.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,网络也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:24.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我已经把放厕所里的Jump读了上百遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:28.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在的年轻人没设备连打发时间都不会了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:32.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在老师那时代是怎么打发时间的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比如思考木纹最像哪个SMAP成员的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再比如找出最像手的窗帘皱褶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很好玩哦  来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:45.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊我已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:47.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要无聊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有什么东西没  有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,纸和铅笔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在画漫画哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:08.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们啊  都来别墅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也让我画画！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:27.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这回超级有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在露营时我做的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好像不太行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:38.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说是太辣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:47.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然咖喱还是爸爸做的最好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个印度厨师究竟是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:56.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是有意装作什么都没思考的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我说  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你有没有什么事情想问爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你说咖喱是什么味道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咖喱不就是咖喱味的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就猜到是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:24.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,或许姬是真的什么事情也没在想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来了  把原稿藏好了  将漫画的味道消除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:49.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs70\c&H6C6669&\pos(913.6,145.6)}创发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我公司的解决方案是这样那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:41.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我是姬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:41.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,技术革新是这样那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,企业条例又是这样那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}哇  爸爸在工作诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天是防灾训练日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:49.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是在避难训练
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我是姬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:54.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没错  让姬知道我是漫画家这件事正是最大的灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:57.04,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(410,74)}不推
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:57.04,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(413.2,362)}不跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:57.04,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(414.8,710.8)}不讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以这当然就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:59.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为了应对万一姬跑到这里来时的突发情况的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.29,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(412.8,68.8)}不放漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.29,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(417.6,368)}不画漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.29,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(409.6,672)}不完成漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我会知道就有鬼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师每年可都少不了这个训练
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下来举行反思会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:07.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,笕君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:08.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你就不能再画可爱点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反思这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那老师你来画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然无论怎么画都比不上真人可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.61,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(700,0)\bord3\pos(312,198.4)}不推
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.61,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(700,0)\bord3\pos(308.8,409.6)}可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.61,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(700,0)\bord3\pos(313.6,627.2)}担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,变态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.12,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz332.4\pos(1564.8,683.2)}不放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.12,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz332.4\pos(1484.8,816)}不画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.12,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz332.4\pos(1424,942.4)}不完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  这个很好吃哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可要好好吃完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊  太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这份可爱无法用画笔来表达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:48.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为了守护这笑容  绝对不能被她发现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我居然在画那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:54.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,稍微等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,急急急急急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十丸院你这家伙  现在赶快滚过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在可不行哦  我现在在北海道出差…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:12.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可不记得我同意过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个我也没同意过  所以没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事个鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你眼前不就是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真没想到就连「风之紧身裤」这种作品都会有山寨周边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你说「就连」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:27.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你要还是个编辑的话就去投诉一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那  那个  关于这些面具…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一点都不受欢迎  完全卖不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:42.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  你完全不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他说完全卖不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,问题不在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有时候会发生这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明并不是很受欢迎的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,却有其山寨周边充斥在市场上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可能是在偶然看到的杂志上的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其作品又偶然的正是杂志封面又是刊头彩页
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就决定是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大概是误认为这是一部很受欢迎的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管了  我自己去交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我全要了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你给我负责  拿着这些东西然后消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:16.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,带着这家伙和这些面具藏起来  可不要被姬发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好慢哦  你去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下来要买什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想吃棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那我们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这有棉花糖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.70,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}风之紧身裤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:36.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再稍微等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:38.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我全要了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:39.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,芥子君  你来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:43.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,搬回去的时候记得可别太引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把所有子弹给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:54.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还是没中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没中  没中  没中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:01.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个面具挺好卖的  明年我要多做10倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要增加5倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明年老师还得把这些东西10倍全部买完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:10.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这时候的他还仍未知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么这个时候会发出警报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道  姬来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,检测我们训练成果的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:25.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,将漫画的味道消除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把所有工具收纳起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,换装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.71,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs70\c&H6C6669&\pos(913.6,145.6)}创发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们是公安警察
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:33.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们接到一起报案说是有多数非特定的男女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,时常携带着大量的食物进行集会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,偷偷摸摸地干着些什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:44.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因此怀疑这里是不是反社会团体的一个据点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,从旁人来看确实有些可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请让我们检查一下里边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么都没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:55.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么  这用塑料口袋装着的大量白色粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这并不是白色粉末只是棉花糖而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你还没吃完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你也不想想这得有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来这个就是你们组织的资金来源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说不定电脑里还有其资料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我这就调查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:12.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:13.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.39,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H625FD3&\pos(619.6,110.8)}漫画家五大素养
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.39,kakushigoto in 9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(702.4,347.2)}电影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.39,kakushigoto in 9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700.8,417.6)}梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.39,kakushigoto in 9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729.6,476.8)}爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.39,kakushigoto in 9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710.4,539.2)}干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.39,kakushigoto in 9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,603.2)}酒会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画姬的面具时所搜索的词语有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:19.68,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\fscx83\fscy98\c&H747476&\pos(672,401.6)}可爱的幼女画法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,恐怕会被误会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,差不多能请回了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然我不太想说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:36.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们其实是漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:40.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你觉得会有这样的漫画工作室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说的好像也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我找到了这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,女性紧身裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:47.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个是作为资料用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你用来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:50.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你问用途？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然是戴在头上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来是抢劫银行时用的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这次还找到了这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然你们是银行抢劫犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是作为资料用的模型枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.26,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934.4,91.2)\c&H3D3D4C&}使用故事情节
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.26,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz270\c&H3D3D48&\pos(492.8,289.6)}主人公紧身裤打出去的球被狙击枪打上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就连日本刀都有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.14,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz270\c&H3C3C49&\pos(1515.2,427.2)}使用故事情节
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.14,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&H3D3D48&\pos(352,177.6)\frz270}使用日本刀在有利位置开洞随后将球轻推入洞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.14,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz270\c&H3D3D48&\pos(307.2,177.6)}出自敌人武士安全裤登场一回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那也是作为资料用的模型刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们就是打算用这个袭击官邸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:11.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫画家们总是会最先买这些东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们已经无法再抵赖了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.82,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H535761&\frz267.2\move(1011.2,48,1094,60)}抢劫时用的连裤袜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.82,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H535761&\frz283.7\move(900.8,417.6,995,425)}壁柜里隐藏着的白色粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:16.28,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H535761&\frz260.2\move(742.4,392,1140,390)}枪械管制刀具等大量武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:16.28,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord2\c&H535761&\frz279.6\move(278.4,35.2,700,78)}在空中散布的无人飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们难道企图推翻这个国家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:20.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我现在好像感觉自己真的是反社会团体的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大致上没什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像我们这样的组织末端
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:29.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说不定在不知不觉中已经参与了犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们自首
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:31.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请逮捕我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂  你们冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师啊  您可是会有好长一段时间见不到姬的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:41.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自首吧  让自己的罪孽减轻一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我承认了  是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:50.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个  这人真的是个漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,少骗人了  你有什么东西能够证明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是我的私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.45,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H16161D&\pos(828.6,895.8)}作者近照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看了你的全裸照片后  好像放过我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反正这东西都已经是出版了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,祭典的那天我好像没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我什么时候给你买了这样的浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这件别人说是手缝的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,穿给邻居家的阿姨看后  阿姨告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是爸爸你缝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在壁橱里找到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:41.24,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(878.4,340.8)\c&H0E0E0E&}10岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这件装在10岁的盒子里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其它的箱子你看了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只看到10岁的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为我才10岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就连16岁的箱子也有  我好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,下次缝一件连衣裙给我好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厉害  爸爸什么都会缝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:11.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那也缝双鞋子给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,鞋子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还要一副眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:17.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,眼镜可不是能缝出来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:19.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人家知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只是觉得爸爸的话  应该就能缝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:25.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且姬你的眼睛也不是不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要的是装饰的眼镜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸你不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了  突然让我教你怎么缝纫东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这些你就别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,终于还是去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交给她钥匙的是小罗砂你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可没这样的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:08.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说起来  真亏能隐瞒到现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:12.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟当事人也不打算了解嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:16.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,父亲的隐瞒之事就是作画工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来到镰仓后  我知晓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,同时也注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:27.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实并不是父亲隐瞒着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是我并不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:38.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大概  是我害怕去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,知道父亲的工作后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:46.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不想知道的事情也得被迫知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉我和父亲快乐的生活会就此破碎
