Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.58,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\c&H898674&\pos(614.4,280)}17岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.58,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\c&H61605C&\pos(601.6,529.6)}18岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.58,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\c&H61605C&\pos(920,278.4)}19岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.58,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\c&H53524E&\pos(923.2,526.4)}20岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:59.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,箱子之中又有些箱子
