Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:36.20,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}将离别的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:46.01,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}ポケットに匿していたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:46.01,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}隐藏在口袋中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:53.10,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}想い出は  モノクローム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:53.10,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}回忆是单色相片
