Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:06.90,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}再一次来到我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:11.91,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}はなやいで  うるわしの Color Girl
